  <main>
	<div class="container">
		<h1>Health</h1>

		<div class="row">
    		<div class="col-sm-6">
    		
    			<h2>Your DVA Health card (White card)</h2>
    			
				<p>You can use your DVA Health card to access health services for the following accepted conditions:</p>
				<ul class="boxed-list-items">
					<li><b>Lumbar spondylosis</b></li>
					<li><b>Sprained ankle</b></li>
				</ul>
				<button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--secondary small" onclick="window.location.href = '/health-card1'">Add mental health treatment to my card</button>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6" style="text-align:center;">
			
				<img src="../../docs/images/healthcard-samplecard.png" width="350">
				<div style="padding-bottom:10px;"><i>Above: an example DVA Health card (White card)</i></div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		
		
	</div>
    <div style="background-color:#f4f4f4; padding:30px 0 60px 0; margin:60px 0 30px 0;">
    	<div class="container">
    		<h2>How to use your Health card</h2>
    		
    		<div class="row">
    			<div class="col-sm-4">
    				<img src="../../docs/images/healthcard-step1.png" width="85%">
    				<p>Confirm with your health care provider that they accept the DVA Health card when making your appointment for treatment. Prior approval from DVA is not generally required. Your provider will make arrangements if prior approval is necessary.</p></div>
				<div class="col-sm-4">
					<img src="../../docs/images/healthcard-step2.png" width="85%">
					<p>Show your physical or digital DVA Health card to your health care provider when receiving treatment.</p>
				</div>
   				<div class="col-sm-4">
   					<img src="../../docs/images/healthcard-step3.png" width="85%">
   					<p>You donâ€™t have to pay for treatment if it relates to any of your approved conditions or any mental health condition.</p>
   					<div style="border:1px solid #666666; padding:1em;">
						If you are billed by your health care provider, <b><u>DO NOT</u></b> pay the account and tell DVA immediately on 555-5555
   					</div>
   				</div>
    		</div>
    		
    	</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-5">
				<h2>Mental health treatment</h2>

				<p>We will pay for your mental health treatment under non-liability health care arrangements. All you need to do is submit a request and we will update your Health card to include mental health treatment.</p>
				<button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--secondary">Access mental health treatment</button>
			</div>
			
			<div class="col-sm-7">
				<h3>How to access free mental health treatment</h3>
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-xs-3">
						<img src="../../docs/images/mentalhealth-step1.png" width="180">
					</div>
					<div class="col-xs-9">
						<p>Use MyService to request free mental health treatment. We will then update your Health card to include mental health treatment.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-xs-3">
						<img src="../../docs/images/mentalhealth-step2.png" width="180">
					</div>
					<div class="col-xs-9">
						<p>Go get treatment.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-xs-3">
						<img src="../../docs/images/mentalhealth-step3.png" width="180">
					</div>
					<div class="col-xs-9">
						<p>Don't pay for treatment. Use your DVA Health card instead.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
 
    
